00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:24.430
I'm not going to cover that in these videos,
e.g. what it's about and what's included and

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:29.180
all of that stuff. Just go to the website.
I've got it all laid out there. It's a long

00:00:29.180 --> 00:00:35.860
letter that explains the whole process. Go
to zerodowninvesting.com. Spell it out -- z

00:00:35.860 --> 00:00:40.590
e r o downinvesting.com and you can find all
of the information about the Mentor Program,

00:00:40.590 --> 00:00:44.079
about the buying events, etc.
